# `bolt-project.yaml` options

This page lists the configuration options that are available in the `bolt-project.yaml` configuration file,
which is supported in the [project directory](configuring_bolt.md).

> **Note:** Bolt projects are experimental and may have breaking changes between minor releases. You
> can read more about Bolt projects in [Experimental features](experimental_features.md#bolt-projects).

